l-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-head-image-vinyl-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-head-image-vinyl-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-head-image-vinyl-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-head-image-vinyl-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-head-image-vinyl-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> has announced a special re-release of &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39; in celebration of its fifth anniversary.</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/dua-lipa-live-at-glastonbury-2024-review-setlist-photos-3770003">Dua Lipa live at Glastonbury: a powerhouse performance to shut down the critics</a></strong></li></ul><p> The re-release is pressed on one yellow splatter vinyl and two traditional black vinyl discs. The 3 LP set includes the album&#39;s original 11 tracks, along with the deluxe &#39;Moonlight&#39; Edition, and the remix album &#39;Club Future Nostalgia&#39;.</p><p> The vinyl set will be released on March 28, almost exactly five years after the album first dropped. The original album&#39;s release was originally meant to be April 3 but was brought forward by a week, coinciding with the beginning of the first COVID-19 lockdown. The album was also leaked, which influenced the decision to move it forward.</p><p> Since its release, &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39; has racked up over 22 billion streams across all platforms worldwide, making it the 7th most streamed album ever globally.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/dua-lipa-cover-interview-2020-if-somebody-told-me-not-to-discuss-issues-im-passionate-about-i-wouldnt-listen-2644409">Speaking to <em>NME</em></a> at the time of its release, Lipa said of its composition: “I felt really confident in my lyrical language and I worked with close friends [this time around] so I wasn&#39;t afraid to be vulnerable in the studio. I knew exactly what I wanted and how to assert myself in a studio and around people.”</p><p> Addressing the decision to move the album forward, while other artists were delaying their albums due to the pandemic she said: “I&#39;m super happy that everybody gets to have [the album]. The response has been really nice and I couldn&#39;t have wanted it to go any other way.” </p><figure id="attachment_3837492" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3837492" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3837492" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1.jpg" alt="Dua Lipa vinyl" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dua-lipa-vinyl-reissue-epress-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3837492" class="wp-caption-text"> Dua Lipa vinyl. Credit: Press</figcaption></figure><p> “Music serves as an escape and I&#39;m hoping that this music just brings some light and joy, and takes away from what&#39;s going on outside.”</p><p> In a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/dua-lipa-future-nostalgia-album-review-2633945">five-star review of &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39;</a> , <em>NME</em> wrote: “When she made this album, the musician couldn&#39;t know just how awful a state the world would be upon it&#39;s released. But that just makes her achieving her mission all the more important. &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39; is a bright, bold collection of pop majesty to dance away your anxieties to… if only for a little while.”</p><p> In other news, Lipa  paid her respects following the <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-mourns-death-of-duolingo-owl-3837466">“death” of the Duolingo owl</a> .</p><p> The announcement of the mascot&#39;s death made reference to her, quipping: “We appreciate you respecting Dua Lipa&#39;s privacy at this time.”</p><p> Now, acknowledging news of his death, Lipa has taken to X/Twitter to pay tribute to the owl. Reposting the news from the official Duolingo page, she added the caption: “Til&#39; death duo part”, along with a broken heart emoji.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-announces-special-fifth-anniversary-vinyl-re-release-of-future-nostalgia-3837491">Dua Lipa announces special fifth anniversary vinyl re-release of &#39;Future Nostalgia&#39;</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
